Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:28.54,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}何だかどうして
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:29.98,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}未来になんぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:31.89,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}何の希望もない期待出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:33.72,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}ような気がして
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:35.17,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}もう随分生きている
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:36.81,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}既視感とテンプレで食傷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:39.87,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}素敵な出来事の気配もない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:40.83,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}残念
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:41.98,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}積んだ経験の因果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:44.17,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}形骸化された神話と退屈な進化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.17,0:11:45.43,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}要は刺激が欲しいんだ
