Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:54.03,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}吸い尽くして
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:56.40,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}あれもこれもどれも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:58.70,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}同じ味がする
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:11:59.41,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}UNDEAD
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:00.78,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}死んじゃいない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:02.66,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}お前とお前の連鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:06.71,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}生きていることとは変わり続けることだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:08.50,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}不幸に甘んじて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:10.04,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}満足するなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:13.88,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}幸せになろうとしないなんて卑怯だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:15.34,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}この世この世は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:16.80,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}奇怪奇怪ファンタジー
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:19.93,ED_JP,,27,0,0,,{\an1\c&HFFFFFF&}次は鬼が出るか蛇が出るか
